   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "from scipy import stats\n",
    "# خواندن فایل CSV\n",
    "df_ = pd.read_csv('exoplanets.csv')\n",
    "df_\n",
    "df_.columns\n",
    "# فرض کنیم df دیتاست شما است و ویژگی‌هایی که در تصاویر آمده‌اند:\n",
    "columns_to_transform = [\n",
    "    'koi_fpflag_ec',\n",
    "    'koi_time0bk', 'koi_impact','ra','dec','koi_kepmag_qt','koi_period', 'koi_duration_qt',\n",
    "    'koi_depth', 'koi_prad', 'koi_insol','koi_steff','koi_slogg','koi_srad'\n",
    "]\n",
    "df= df_[columns_to_transform]\n",
    "\n",
    "df\n",
    "\n",
    "df_orginal=df.copy()\n",
    "df"
   ]
  },

    "# 3. محاسبه و رسم نقشه همبستگی پیرسون (Pearson Correlation Heatmap)\n",

    "sns.heatmap(corr, annot=True, cmap='coolwarm')\n",
    "plt.title('Heatmap of Pearson Correlation')\n",
    "plt.show"
   ]

   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "from sklearn.preprocessing import QuantileTransformer\n",
    "\n",
    "# 1. انتخاب ویژگی‌هایی که skewness یا kurtosis بالایی دارند\n",
    "columns_to_fix = skewness[abs(skewness) > 0.5].index.tolist()\n",
    "\n",
    "# 2. روش‌های مختلف برای تصحیح چولگی (Skewness) و کشیدگی (Kurtosis)\n",
    "\n",
    "# روش اول: log transformation (برای داده‌های مثبت)\n",
    "for column in columns_to_fix:\n",
    "    df[column + '_log'] = np.log1p(df[column])  # log(1+x) برای داده‌های صفر و مثبت\n",
    "\n",
    "# روش دوم: Quantile transformation (توزیع داده‌ها را نرمال می‌کند)\n",
    "qt = QuantileTransformer(output_distribution='normal')\n",
    "for column in columns_to_fix:\n",
    "    df[column +'_qt'] = qt.fit_transform(df[[column]])"
   ]
  },
